325 static uint32_t AoAProcDSP_XYZestimation

331  int32_t dopplerSignIdx
332 )

338  float limitScale;

341  DPU_AoAProcDSP_HW_Resources *res = &aoaDspObj->res;
342  DPIF_CFARDetList *objIn = res->cfarRngDopSnrList;
343  DPIF_PointCloudCartesian *objOut = res->detObjOut;

348

350 
351  /* Compensate for range bias */

353  if (range < 0)
354  {
355  range = 0;
356  }
357 
358  if(maxIdx > (DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS/2 -1))
359  {

361  }
362  else
363  {
364  sMaxIdx = maxIdx;
365  }
366 
367  Wx = 2 * (float) sMaxIdx / DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS;
368  /* Check if it is within configured field of view */
369 
370  x = range * Wx;
371 
372  if (params->numVirtualAntElev > 0)
373  {
374  peakAzimIm = (float) azimuthFftOut[maxIdx].imag;
375  peakAzimRe = (float) azimuthFftOut[maxIdx].real;

378 
379  Wz = atan2(peakAzimIm * peakElevRe - peakAzimRe * peakElevIm,
380  peakAzimRe * peakElevRe + peakAzimIm * peakElevIm)/PI_ + (2 * Wx);
381 
382  if (Wz > 1)
383  {
384  Wz = Wz - 2;
385  }
386  else if (Wz < -1)
387  {
388  Wz = Wz + 2;
389  }
390  /* Check if it is within configured field of view */
391  if((Wz < aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.fovAoaLocalCfg.minElevationSineVal) || (Wz > aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.fovAoaLocalCfg.maxElevationSineVal))
392  {
393  goto exit;
394  }
395 
396  z = range * Wz;
397  /*record wz for debugging/testing*/
398  res->detObjElevationAngle[objOutIdx] = Wz;
399  limitScale = sqrt(1 - Wz*Wz);
400  }
401  else
402  {
403  z = 0;
404  limitScale = 1;
405  }
406 
407  if((Wx < (limitScale * aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.fovAoaLocalCfg.minAzimuthSineVal)) ||
408  (Wx > (limitScale * aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.fovAoaLocalCfg.maxAzimuthSineVal)))
409  {
410  goto exit;
411  }
412 
413  temp = range*range -x*x -z*z;
414  if (temp > 0)
415  {
416  y = sqrt(temp);
417  }
418  else
419  {
420  goto exit;
421  }
422 
423  objOut[objOutIdx].x = x;
424  objOut[objOutIdx].y = y;
425  objOut[objOutIdx].z = z;
426 
427  objOut[objOutIdx].velocity = params->dopplerStep * dopplerSignIdx;
428  objOutSideInfo[objOutIdx].noise = objIn[objInCfarIdx].noise;
429  objOutSideInfo[objOutIdx].snr = objIn[objInCfarIdx].snr;
430  res->detObj2dAzimIdx[objOutIdx] = maxIdx;
431 
432  objOutIdx++;
433 
434 exit:
435  return (objOutIdx);
436 }

456 static void AoAProcDSP_dopplerComp
457 (
458  cmplx32ReIm_t *in,
459  cmplx32ReIm_t *out,
460  float Cos,
461  float Sin
462 )
463 {
464  float yRe, yIm;
465 
466  /* Rotate symbol (correct the phase) */
467  yRe = in->real * Cos + in->imag * Sin;

501 static void AoAProcDSP_dopplerCompensation
502 (
503  cmplx32ReIm_t *srcPtr,
504  cmplx32ReIm_t *dstPtr,
505  int32_t dopplerSignIdx,
506  uint32_t numTxAnt,
507  uint32_t numRxAnt,
508  uint32_t numVirtualAntAzim,
509  uint32_t numVirtualAntElev,
510  uint32_t numDopplerBins,
511  uint32_t extendedMaxVelEnabled
512 )
513 {
514  uint32_t hypothesisIdx, j;
515  float dopplerCompensationIdx;
516  int32_t wrapInd;
517  uint32_t numHypotheses;
518  float Cos,Sin,temp;
519  uint32_t numVirtualAnt;
520  uint32_t virtAntIdx;
521  uint32_t txAntIdx;
522 
523 
524  if(extendedMaxVelEnabled)
525  {
526  numHypotheses = numTxAnt;
527  wrapInd = - ((int32_t) (numHypotheses >> 1)); /* e.g. 2tx or 3tx: wrapInd = -1 */
528  if (!(numTxAnt & 0x1) && (dopplerSignIdx < 0)) /* e.g.2 tx, doppler < 0: wrapInd = 0 */
529  {
530  wrapInd++;
531  }
532  }
533  else
534  {
535  numHypotheses = 1;
536  wrapInd = 0;
537  }
538 
539  numVirtualAnt = numVirtualAntAzim + numVirtualAntElev;
540 
541  for(hypothesisIdx = 0; hypothesisIdx < numHypotheses; hypothesisIdx++)
542  {
543  virtAntIdx = 0;
544  /* transfer data corresponding to azimuth virtual antennas (corresponding to chirp of antenna Tx0) */
545  for(j = 0; j < numRxAnt; j++) /* directly copy from source */
546  {
547  dstPtr[virtAntIdx + hypothesisIdx*numVirtualAnt] = srcPtr[virtAntIdx];
548  virtAntIdx++;
549  }
550 
551  if(numTxAnt > 1)
552  {
553  dopplerCompensationIdx = (dopplerSignIdx + (wrapInd * (int32_t)numDopplerBins)) / (float)numTxAnt;
554  Cos = cossp(2*PI_*dopplerCompensationIdx/numDopplerBins);
555  Sin = sinsp(2*PI_*dopplerCompensationIdx/numDopplerBins);
556 
557  for(txAntIdx=1; txAntIdx < numTxAnt; txAntIdx++)
558  {
559  for(j = 0; j < numRxAnt; j++)
560  {
561  AoAProcDSP_dopplerComp(&srcPtr[virtAntIdx], &dstPtr[virtAntIdx + hypothesisIdx*numVirtualAnt], Cos, Sin);
562  virtAntIdx++;
563  }
564  if (txAntIdx < (numTxAnt-1))
565  {
566  /* Increment Doppler phase shift */
567  temp = Cos * Cos - Sin * Sin;
568  Sin = 2 * Cos * Sin;
569  Cos = temp;
570  }
571  }
572  } /* if numTxAnt > 1 */
573 
574  wrapInd++;
575  }/* for numHypotheses */
576 
577 } /* AoAProcDSP_dopplerCompensation */

681 static inline void AoAProcDSP_azimuthHeatMapDecodeBPM
682 (
683  cmplx16ImRe_t *bpmAPtr,/*ping*/
684  cmplx16ImRe_t *bpmBPtr,/*pong*/
685  uint16_t numSymbols
686 )
687 {
688  int16_t real, imag;
689  uint16_t idx;
690 
691  /*We now have Ping and Pong available.
692  Do BPM decoding in place:
693  A=S1+S2 (PING)
694  B=S1-S2 (PONG)
695  Compute S1=(A+B)/2 and overwrite A with this value
696  Compute S2=(A-B)/2 and overwrite B with this value
697  */
698  for(idx = 0; idx < numSymbols; idx++)
699  {
700  /* Note there is no need to do doppler correction because
701  heatmap is computed using doppler bin zero.*/
702 
703  /*first make a copy of A*/
704  real = bpmAPtr[idx].real;
705  imag = bpmAPtr[idx].imag;
706  /*compute S1 and store in A*/
707  bpmAPtr[idx].real = (bpmAPtr[idx].real + bpmBPtr[idx].real)/2;
708  bpmAPtr[idx].imag = (bpmAPtr[idx].imag + bpmBPtr[idx].imag)/2;
709  /*compute S2 and store in B*/
710  bpmBPtr[idx].real = (real - bpmBPtr[idx].real)/2;
711  bpmBPtr[idx].imag = (imag - bpmBPtr[idx].imag)/2;
712  }
713 }

836  }

843  {

845  {

848  retVal = AoAProcDSP_waitInData (res, pingPongIdx);
849  if(retVal != 0)

852  }

854

856  nextTransferTxIdx = txAntIdx + 1;
857  nextTransferRxIdx = rxAntIdx;
858  nextTransferRangeIdx = rangeIdx;
859

861  {
862  nextTransferTxIdx = 0;
863  nextTransferRxIdx++;
864  if(nextTransferRxIdx == DPParams->numRxAntennas)
865  {
866  nextTransferRxIdx = 0;
867  nextTransferRangeIdx++;
868  }
869  }
870 
871  nextTransferIdx = (nextTransferTxIdx * DPParams->numRxAntennas * DPParams->numDopplerChirps +
872  nextTransferRxIdx) * DPParams->numRangeBins + nextTransferRangeIdx;
873 
874  /*Last computation happens when nextTransferRangeIdx reaches numRangeBins.
875  This indicates that, the current virtual antenna is the last one for (numRangeBins-1).
876  Therefore, do not trigger next EDMA.*/
877  if(nextTransferRangeIdx < DPParams->numRangeBins)
878  {
879  /* kick off next DMA */
880  if (pingPongIdx == DPU_AOAPROCDSP_PONG_IDX)
881  {
882  channel = res->edmaPing.channel;
883  }
884  else
885  {
886  channel = res->edmaPong.channel;
887  }
888 
889  retVal = EDMA_setSourceAddress(res->edmaHandle, channel,
890  (uint32_t) &radarCubeBase[nextTransferIdx]);
891  if (retVal != 0)
892  {
893  goto exit;
894  }
895 
896  EDMA_startDmaTransfer(res->edmaHandle, channel);
897  }
898 
899  inpBuf = (cmplx16ImRe_t *) &res->pingPongBuf[pingPongIdx * DPParams->numDopplerChirps];
900 
901  /* Remove static clutter? */
902  if (aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.staticClutterCfg.isEnabled)
903  {
904  AoAProcDSP_clutterRemoval(DPParams, inpBuf);
905  }
906 
907  if(DPParams->isBpmEnabled)
908  {
909  /*If BPM is enabled, need to store 2 sets of
910  doppler bins (1 ping + 1 pong) so that BPM decoding can be done later on.
911  The order of the EDMA assures that consecutive ping/pong buffers have the correct
912  data for BPM decoding.*/
913 
914  if(pingPongIdx == DPU_AOAPROCDSP_PING_IDX)
915  {
916  memcpy((void*)&bpmPingBuff[0], inpBuf, DPParams->numDopplerChirps * sizeof(cmplx16ImRe_t));
917 
918  /*Store ping indexes to be used later when both ping and pong are available.*/
919  rxAntIdxPing = rxAntIdx;
920  txAntIdxPing = txAntIdx;
921  }
922  else
923  {
924  /*Decode BPM*/
925  AoAProcDSP_azimuthHeatMapDecodeBPM(bpmPingBuff,/*Ping data*/
926  inpBuf, /*Pong data*/
927  DPParams->numDopplerChirps);
928 
929  /* Compute heatmap value from ping data*/
930  AoAProcDSP_computeHeatMapVal(aoaDspObj,
931  bpmPingBuff,
932  rxAntIdxPing,
933  txAntIdxPing,
934  rangeIdx);
935 
936  /* Compute heatmap value from pong data*/
937  AoAProcDSP_computeHeatMapVal(aoaDspObj,
938  inpBuf,
939  rxAntIdx,
940  txAntIdx,
941  rangeIdx);
942  }
943  }
944  else
945  {/*BPM not enabled*/
946 
947  AoAProcDSP_computeHeatMapVal(aoaDspObj,
948  inpBuf,
949  rxAntIdx,
950  txAntIdx,
951  rangeIdx);
952  }
953 
954  pingPongIdx ^= 1;
955  }/*txAntIdx*/
956  } /* rxAntIdx */
957  }/*rangeIdx*/
958 
959 exit:
960  return retVal;
961 }

1025 static inline void AoAProcDSP_decodeBPM(cmplx32ReIm_t *virtAntennaBuf, uint16_t numRxAnt)
1026 {
1027  cmplx32ReIm_t *bpmAPtr;
1028  cmplx32ReIm_t *bpmBPtr;
1029  int32_t real, imag, idx;
1030 
1031  bpmAPtr = &virtAntennaBuf[0];
1032  bpmBPtr = &virtAntennaBuf[numRxAnt];
1033 
1034  for(idx = 0; idx < numRxAnt; idx++)
1035  {
1036  /*BPM decoding*/
1037  /*store A*/
1038  real = bpmAPtr[idx].real;
1039  imag = bpmAPtr[idx].imag;
1040  /*compute S1 and store in place*/
1041  bpmAPtr[idx].real = (bpmAPtr[idx].real + bpmBPtr[idx].real)/2;
1042  bpmAPtr[idx].imag = (bpmAPtr[idx].imag + bpmBPtr[idx].imag)/2;
1043  /*compute S2 and store in place*/
1044  bpmBPtr[idx].real = (real - bpmBPtr[idx].real)/2;
1045  bpmBPtr[idx].imag = (imag - bpmBPtr[idx].imag)/2;
1046  }
1047 }

1067 static inline uint32_t AoAProcDSP_processMultipleVirtualAntennas
1068 (
1069  AOADspObj *aoaDspObj,
1070  uint32_t numObjsIn,
1071  uint32_t *numObjsOut,
1072  volatile uint32_t *waitTime
1073 )
1074 {
1075  uint16_t idx, rxAntIdx, rangeIdx, txAntIdx, dopplerIdx;
1076  uint16_t nextTransferRxIdx, nextTransferRangeIdx, nextTransferTxIdx;
1077  DPU_AoAProcDSP_HW_Resources *res;
1078  DPU_AoAProcDSP_StaticConfig *DPParams;
1079  cmplx16ImRe_t *inpDoppFftBuf;
1080  cmplx32ReIm_t elevationSymbols[SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL];
1081  uint32_t numObjsOutLocal = 0;
1082  volatile uint32_t startTimeWait;
1083  int32_t retVal = 0;
1084  cmplx16ImRe_t *radarCubeBase;
1085  uint32_t pingPongIdx, nextTransferIdx;
1086  uint8_t channel;
1087  cmplx32ReIm_t *windowingBuf;
1088  cmplx32ReIm_t *azimuthFftOut;
1089  cmplx32ReIm_t *twoDfftOut;
1090  /* for extMaxVelocity feature: */
1091  cmplx32ReIm_t *hypothesesSymbols;
1092  cmplx32ReIm_t *azimuthFftOutTemp;
1093  int32_t dopplerSignIdx;
1094  int32_t hypIdx, maxHypIdx;
1095  float32_t maxPow, maxPowTemp;
1096  int32_t wrapStartInd;
1097 
1098 
1099  res = &aoaDspObj->res;
1100  DPParams = &aoaDspObj->params;
1101  radarCubeBase = (cmplx16ImRe_t *)res->radarCube.data;
1102  /* Setup overlayed buffers */
1103  windowingBuf = (cmplx32ReIm_t *)res->scratch1Buff;
1104  azimuthFftOut = (cmplx32ReIm_t *)res->scratch1Buff;
1105  twoDfftOut = (cmplx32ReIm_t *)res->scratch2Buff;
1106  /* Setup overlayed buffers for extMaxVelocity feature */
1107  hypothesesSymbols = (cmplx32ReIm_t *)res->scratch2Buff;
1108  azimuthFftOutTemp = res->elevationFftOut;
1109 
1110  /* Angle estimation for each object */
1111  for (idx = 0; idx < numObjsIn; idx++)
1112  {
1113  rangeIdx = res->cfarRngDopSnrList[idx].rangeIdx;
1114  dopplerIdx = res->cfarRngDopSnrList[idx].dopplerIdx;
1115 
1116  /* Reset ping/pong index */
1117  pingPongIdx = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_PING_IDX;
1118 
1119  /* Trigger first DMA. First transfer is for [txAntIdx=0, rxAntIdx=0, rangeIdx=(Obj range from CFAR list)].
1120  Note: EDMA ping/pong scheme must support #TX antennas = 1,2,3 #RX antennas = 2,4 */
1121  retVal = EDMA_setSourceAddress(res->edmaHandle,
1122  res->edmaPing.channel,
1123  (uint32_t) &radarCubeBase[rangeIdx]);
1124  if (retVal != 0)
1125  {
1126  goto exit;
1127  }
1128 
1129  EDMA_startDmaTransfer(res->edmaHandle, res->edmaPing.channel);
1130 
1131  for (rxAntIdx = 0; rxAntIdx < DPParams->numRxAntennas; rxAntIdx++)
1132  {
1133  for (txAntIdx = 0; txAntIdx < DPParams->numTxAntennas; txAntIdx++)
1134  {
1135  /* verify that previous DMA has completed */
1136  startTimeWait = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp();
1137  retVal = AoAProcDSP_waitInData (res, pingPongIdx);
1138  if(retVal != 0)
1139  {
1140  goto exit;
1141  }
1142 
1143  *waitTime += Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp() - startTimeWait;
1144 
1145  /*Find index in radar cube for next EDMA.*/
1146  nextTransferTxIdx = txAntIdx + 1;
1147  nextTransferRxIdx = rxAntIdx;
1148  nextTransferRangeIdx = rangeIdx;
1149 
1150  if(nextTransferTxIdx == DPParams->numTxAntennas)
1151  {
1152  nextTransferTxIdx = 0;
1153  nextTransferRxIdx++;
1154  if(nextTransferRxIdx == DPParams->numRxAntennas)
1155  {
1156  nextTransferRxIdx = 0;
1157  nextTransferRangeIdx++;
1158  }
1159  }
1160 
1161  nextTransferIdx = (nextTransferTxIdx * DPParams->numRxAntennas * DPParams->numDopplerChirps +
1162  nextTransferRxIdx) * DPParams->numRangeBins + nextTransferRangeIdx;
1163 
1164  /*Last computation happens when nextTransferRangeIdx reaches (rangeIdx + 1) was we are processing
1165  only one range index. Therefore, do not trigger next EDMA.*/
1166  if(nextTransferRangeIdx == rangeIdx)
1167  {
1168  /* kick off next DMA */
1169  if (pingPongIdx == DPU_AOAPROCDSP_PONG_IDX)
1170  {
1171  channel = res->edmaPing.channel;
1172  }
1173  else
1174  {
1175  channel = res->edmaPong.channel;
1176  }
1177 
1178  retVal = EDMA_setSourceAddress(res->edmaHandle, channel,
1179  (uint32_t) &radarCubeBase[nextTransferIdx]);
1180  if (retVal != 0)
1181  {
1182  goto exit;
1183  }
1184 
1185  EDMA_startDmaTransfer(res->edmaHandle, channel);
1186  }
1187 
1188  inpDoppFftBuf = (cmplx16ImRe_t *) &res->pingPongBuf[pingPongIdx * DPParams->numDopplerChirps];
1189 
1190  /* Remove static clutter? */
1191  if (aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.staticClutterCfg.isEnabled)
1192  {
1193  AoAProcDSP_clutterRemoval(DPParams, inpDoppFftBuf);
1194  }
1195 
1196  /* The windowing output buffer is the input buffer for the Doppler FFT.
1197  It needs to be padded with zeroes if number of Doppler chirps is less than
1198  the number of Doppler bins.*/
1199  if(DPParams->numDopplerBins > DPParams->numDopplerChirps)
1200  {
1201  memset((void*)(&windowingBuf[DPParams->numDopplerChirps]), 0,
1202  (DPParams->numDopplerBins - DPParams->numDopplerChirps) * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1203  }
1204 
1205  /*Up to this point samples are in ImRe format, which is the radar cube format.
1206  The windowing function will do IQ swap and the Doppler FFT is computed in
1207  ReIm format.*/
1208  mmwavelib_windowing16x32_IQswap((int16_t *) inpDoppFftBuf,
1209  res->windowCoeff,
1210  (int32_t *) windowingBuf,
1211  DPParams->numDopplerChirps);
1212 
1213  /*From this point forward samples are in ReIm format. In particular, FFT, twiddle are all in ReIm format.*/
1214 
1215  /*DSPLIB notes for DSP_fft32x32():
1216  Minimum FFT size is 16. Size must be power of 2.
1217  No scaling done in FFT computation.*/
1218  DSP_fft32x32((int32_t *)res->twiddle32x32,
1219  DPParams->numDopplerBins,
1220  (int32_t *)windowingBuf,
1221  (int32_t *)twoDfftOut);
1222 
1223  /* Save the 2D doppler FFT output for the required doppler bin */
1224  res->angleFftIn[txAntIdx * DPParams->numRxAntennas + rxAntIdx] = twoDfftOut[dopplerIdx];
1225 
1226  pingPongIdx ^= 1;
1227  }/*txAntIdx*/
1228  } /* rxAntIdx */
1229 
1230  dopplerSignIdx = AOA_DOPPLER_IDX_TO_SIGNED(dopplerIdx, DPParams->numDopplerBins);
1231 
1232  if(!aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.extMaxVelCfg.enabled || DPParams->numTxAntennas==1)
1233  {
1234  /* When BPM is enabled, order must be:
1235  2D FFT -> Doppler compensation -> BPM decoding -> RX phase compensation */
1236 
1237  /* Doppler compensation. */
1238  AoAProcDSP_dopplerCompensation(
1239  &res->angleFftIn[0],
1240  &res->angleFftIn[0],
1241  dopplerSignIdx,
1242  DPParams->numTxAntennas,
1243  DPParams->numRxAntennas,
1244  DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim,
1245  DPParams->numVirtualAntElev,
1246  DPParams->numDopplerBins,
1247  aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.extMaxVelCfg.enabled);
1248 
1249  if(DPParams->isBpmEnabled)
1250  {/* BPM decoding*/
1251  AoAProcDSP_decodeBPM(&res->angleFftIn[0], DPParams->numRxAntennas);
1252  }
1253 
1254  /* RX channel gain/phase offset compensation. */
1255  AoAProcDSP_rxChanPhaseBiasCompensation(&aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.compRxChanCfg.rxChPhaseComp[0],
1256  DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim + DPParams->numVirtualAntElev,
1257  &res->angleFftIn[0],
1258  &res->angleFftIn[0]);
1259 
1260  /* Save elevation symbols before doing Azimuth FFT.*/
1261  if(DPParams->numVirtualAntElev > 0)
1262  {
1263  memcpy((void*)&elevationSymbols[0],
1264  (void*)&res->angleFftIn[DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim],
1265  DPParams->numVirtualAntElev * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1266  }
1267 
1268  /* Zero padding */
1269  memset((void *) &res->angleFftIn[DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim], 0,
1270  (DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS - DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim) * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1271 
1272  /* 3D-FFT (Azimuth FFT) */
1273  DSP_fft32x32((int32_t *)res->angleTwiddle32x32,
1274  DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS,
1275  (int32_t *) &res->angleFftIn[0],
1276  (int32_t *) &azimuthFftOut[0]);
1277 
1278  /* Perform 3D elevation FFT if elevation virtual antennas are present*/
1279  if(DPParams->numVirtualAntElev > 0)
1280  {
1281  /* Restore elevation symbols to FFT input buffer */
1282  memcpy((void*)&res->angleFftIn[0],
1283  (void*)&elevationSymbols[0],
1284  DPParams->numVirtualAntElev * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1285 
1286  /* Zero padding */
1287  memset((void *) &res->angleFftIn[DPParams->numVirtualAntElev], 0,
1288  (DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS - DPParams->numVirtualAntElev) * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1289 
1290  /* 3D-FFT (Elevation FFT) */
1291  DSP_fft32x32((int32_t *)res->angleTwiddle32x32,
1292  DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS,
1293  (int32_t *) &res->angleFftIn[0],
1294  (int32_t *) &res->elevationFftOut[0]);
1295  }
1296  }/* if extMaxVel disabled */
1297 
1298  if(DPParams->numTxAntennas>1 && aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.extMaxVelCfg.enabled)
1299  {
1300  /* RX channel gain/phase offset compensation. */
1301  AoAProcDSP_rxChanPhaseBiasCompensation(&aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.compRxChanCfg.rxChPhaseComp[0],
1302  DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim + DPParams->numVirtualAntElev,
1303  &res->angleFftIn[0],
1304  &res->angleFftIn[0]);
1305 
1306  /* Doppler compensation, produce compensated symbols for all Doppler hypotheses. */
1307  AoAProcDSP_dopplerCompensation(
1308  &res->angleFftIn[0],
1309  &hypothesesSymbols[0],
1310  dopplerSignIdx,
1311  DPParams->numTxAntennas,
1312  DPParams->numRxAntennas,
1313  DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim,
1314  DPParams->numVirtualAntElev,
1315  DPParams->numDopplerBins,
1316  aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.extMaxVelCfg.enabled);
1317 
1318  /* Perform 3D Azimuth FFT for each Doppler hypothesis and pick the one with highest peak power. */
1319  maxPow = 0;
1320  maxHypIdx = 0;
1321  for (hypIdx = 0; hypIdx < DPParams->numTxAntennas; hypIdx++)
1322  {
1323  /* Copy azimuth symbols of this hypothesis to angleFftIn buffer */
1324  memcpy((void*)&res->angleFftIn[0],
1325  (void*)&hypothesesSymbols[hypIdx*(DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim + DPParams->numVirtualAntElev)],
1326  DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1327  /* Zero padding */
1328  memset((void *) &res->angleFftIn[DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim], 0,
1329  (DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS - DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim) * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1330 
1331  /* 3D-FFT (Azimuth FFT) on this hypothesis*/
1332  DSP_fft32x32((int32_t *)res->angleTwiddle32x32,
1333  DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS,
1334  (int32_t *) &res->angleFftIn[0],
1335  (int32_t *) &azimuthFftOutTemp[0]);
1336 
1337  /* peak power search on Azimuth FFT output of this hypothesis. */
1338  mmwavelib_maxpow((int32_t *) &azimuthFftOutTemp[0],
1339  DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS,
1340  &maxPowTemp);
1341 
1342  /* if this hypothesis has higher peak power, store its index and its Azimuth FFT output*/
1343  if (maxPowTemp > maxPow)
1344  {
1345  maxPow = maxPowTemp;
1346  maxHypIdx = hypIdx;
1347  /* Copy from temp buffer to final Azimuth FFT output buffer.*/
1348  memcpy((void*)&azimuthFftOut[0],
1349  (void*)&azimuthFftOutTemp[0],
1350  DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1351  }
1352  }/* loop of all Doppler hypotheses */
1353 
1354  /* If elevation virtual antennas are present, perform 3D elevation FFT for the picked Doppler hypothesis. */
1355  if(DPParams->numVirtualAntElev > 0)
1356  {
1357  /* Copy elevation symbols to FFT input buffer */
1358  memcpy((void*)&res->angleFftIn[0],
1359  (void*)&hypothesesSymbols[maxHypIdx*(DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim+DPParams->numVirtualAntElev)+DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim],
1360  DPParams->numVirtualAntElev * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1361 
1362  /* Zero padding */
1363  memset((void *) &res->angleFftIn[DPParams->numVirtualAntElev], 0,
1364  (DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS - DPParams->numVirtualAntElev) * sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t));
1365 
1366  /* 3D-FFT (Elevation FFT) */
1367  DSP_fft32x32((int32_t *)res->angleTwiddle32x32,
1368  DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS,
1369  (int32_t *) &res->angleFftIn[0],
1370  (int32_t *) &res->elevationFftOut[0]);
1371  }
1372 
1373  wrapStartInd = - ((int32_t) (DPParams->numTxAntennas >> 1));
1374  if (!(DPParams->numTxAntennas & 0x1) && (dopplerSignIdx < 0))
1375  {
1376  wrapStartInd++;
1377  }
1378  /* the signed Doppler index of the picked Doppler hypothesis */
1379  dopplerSignIdx += (wrapStartInd + maxHypIdx) * (int32_t) DPParams->numDopplerBins;
1380 
1381  }/*extMaxVelCfg.enabled and numTx>1*/
1382 
1383  /* Angle estimation*/
1384  numObjsOutLocal = AoAProcDSP_angleEstimationAzimElev(aoaDspObj,
1385  idx,
1386  numObjsOutLocal,
1387  dopplerSignIdx);
1388 
1389  if(numObjsOutLocal >= res->detObjOutMaxSize)
1390  {
1391  /*Stop processing CFAR list as the limit for number of detected objects was reached*/
1392  goto exit;
1393  }
1394 
1395  }/* for (idx = 0; idx < numObjsIn; idx++) */
1396 
1397 exit:
1398  *numObjsOut = numObjsOutLocal;
1399  return retVal;
1400 }

1429 int32_t DPU_AoAProcDSP_config
1430 (
1431  DPU_AoAProcDSP_Handle handle,
1432  DPU_AoAProcDSP_Config *aoaDspCfg
1433 )
1434 {
1435  int32_t retVal = 0;
1436  AOADspObj *aoaDspObj = (AOADspObj *)handle;
1437 
1438  if((aoaDspObj == NULL) || (aoaDspCfg == NULL))
1439  {
1440  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1441  goto exit;
1442  }
1443 
1444  /* Check if radar cube formats are supported. */
1445  if (!(aoaDspCfg->res.radarCube.datafmt == DPIF_RADARCUBE_FORMAT_1))
1446  {
1447  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL__RADARCUBE_DATAFORMAT;
1448  goto exit;
1449  }
1450 
1451  /* Check if number of doppler bins is at least 16 (due to DSPLIB which requires size of FFT to be
1452  at least 16*/
1453  if(aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numDopplerBins < 16)
1454  {
1455  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_ENUMDOPBINS;
1456  goto exit;
1457  }
1458 
1459  /* Check if number of doppler chirps is a multiple of 4. Limitation of mmwavelib */
1460  if((aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numDopplerChirps & 3) != 0)
1461  {
1462  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_ENUMDOPCHIRPS;
1463  goto exit;
1464  }
1465 
1466  /* Check if DPU configuration is compatible with EDMA max jump size of (32K - 1)*/
1467  if(aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numRxAntennas * aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numRangeBins * sizeof(cmplx16ImRe_t) >= 32768)
1468  {
1469  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EEXCEEDMAXEDMA;
1470  goto exit;
1471  }
1472 
1473  /* Validate buffers and params */
1474  if(!aoaDspCfg->res.edmaHandle ||
1475  !aoaDspCfg->res.cfarRngDopSnrList ||
1476  !aoaDspCfg->res.detObjOut ||
1477  !aoaDspCfg->res.detObjOutSideInfo ||
1478  !aoaDspCfg->res.detObj2dAzimIdx ||
1479  (!aoaDspCfg->res.detObjElevationAngle && (aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numVirtualAntElev > 0)) ||
1480  (!aoaDspCfg->res.azimuthStaticHeatMap && aoaDspCfg->dynCfg.prepareRangeAzimuthHeatMap) ||
1481  !aoaDspCfg->res.windowCoeff ||
1482  !aoaDspCfg->res.pingPongBuf ||
1483  !aoaDspCfg->res.angleTwiddle32x32 ||
1484  !aoaDspCfg->res.twiddle32x32 ||
1485  !aoaDspCfg->res.angleFftIn ||
1486  (!aoaDspCfg->res.elevationFftOut && (aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numVirtualAntElev > 0)) ||
1487  !aoaDspCfg->res.scratch1Buff ||
1488  !aoaDspCfg->res.scratch2Buff
1489  )
1490  {
1491  retVal= DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1492  goto exit;
1493  }
1494 
1495  if (MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.cfarRngDopSnrList,
1496  DPU_AOAPROCDSP_CFAR_DET_LIST_BYTE_ALIGNMENT))
1497  {
1498  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_CFAR_DET_LIST;
1499  goto exit;
1500  }
1501 
1502  if (MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.detObjOut,
1503  DPU_AOAPROCDSP_POINT_CLOUD_CARTESIAN_BYTE_ALIGNMENT))
1504  {
1505  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_POINT_CLOUD_CARTESIAN;
1506  goto exit;
1507  }
1508 
1509  if (MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.detObjOutSideInfo,
1510  DPU_AOAPROCDSP_POINT_CLOUD_SIDE_INFO_BYTE_ALIGNMENT))
1511  {
1512  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_POINT_CLOUD_SIDE_INFO;
1513  goto exit;
1514  }
1515 
1516  /* Check if buffers provided by application have the correct alignment*/
1517  if (MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.detObjElevationAngle, DPU_AOAPROCDSP_DET_OBJ_ELEVATION_ANGLE_BYTE_ALIGNMENT) ||

1519  MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.windowCoeff, DPU_AOAPROCDSP_BUFFERS_BYTE_ALIGNMENT) ||
1520  MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.pingPongBuf , DPU_AOAPROCDSP_BUFFERS_BYTE_ALIGNMENT) ||
1521  MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.angleTwiddle32x32, DPU_AOAPROCDSP_BUFFERS_BYTE_ALIGNMENT) ||
1522  MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.twiddle32x32, DPU_AOAPROCDSP_BUFFERS_BYTE_ALIGNMENT) ||
1523  MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.angleFftIn, DPU_AOAPROCDSP_BUFFERS_BYTE_ALIGNMENT) ||
1524  MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.elevationFftOut, DPU_AOAPROCDSP_BUFFERS_BYTE_ALIGNMENT) ||
1525  MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.scratch1Buff, DPU_AOAPROCDSP_BUFFERS_BYTE_ALIGNMENT) ||
1526  MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(aoaDspCfg->res.scratch2Buff, DPU_AOAPROCDSP_BUFFERS_BYTE_ALIGNMENT))
1527  {
1528  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_BUFF;
1529  goto exit;
1530  }
1531 
1532  /* check sizes for the scratch buffers provided by application */
1533  if((aoaDspCfg->res.windowSize < (sizeof(int32_t) * aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numDopplerChirps) / 2) ||
1534  (aoaDspCfg->res.pingPongSize < 2 * sizeof(cmplx16ImRe_t) * aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numDopplerChirps) ||
1535  (aoaDspCfg->res.angleTwiddleSize < sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t) * DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS) ||
1536  (aoaDspCfg->res.twiddleSize < sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t) * aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numDopplerBins) ||
1537  (aoaDspCfg->res.angleFftInSize < sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t) * DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS) ||
1538  (aoaDspCfg->res.elevationFftOutSize < sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t) * DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS) ||
1539  (aoaDspCfg->res.scratch1Size < MAX(sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t) * aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numDopplerBins,
1540  sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t) * DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS)) ||
1541  (aoaDspCfg->res.scratch2Size < MAX(sizeof(cmplx32ReIm_t) * aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numDopplerBins,
1542  sizeof(float) * DPU_AOAPROCDSP_NUM_ANGLE_BINS)))
1543  {

1545  goto exit;
1546  }
1547 
1548  /* Check Heatmap configuration */
1549  if (aoaDspCfg->dynCfg.prepareRangeAzimuthHeatMap)
1550  {
1551  if (aoaDspCfg->res.azimuthStaticHeatMapSize !=
1552  (aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numRangeBins * aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numVirtualAntAzim))

1555  goto exit;
1556  }
1557  }
1558 
1559  if (aoaDspCfg->dynCfg.prepareRangeAzimuthHeatMap && (aoaDspCfg->staticCfg.numVirtualAntAzim == 1))
1560  {
1561  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVALID_NUM_VIRT_ANT_AND_AZIMUTH_STATIC_HEAT_MAP;
1562  goto exit;
1563  }
1564 
1565  aoaDspObj->res = aoaDspCfg->res;
1566  aoaDspObj->params = aoaDspCfg->staticCfg;
1567 
1568  aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.compRxChanCfg = *aoaDspCfg->dynCfg.compRxChanCfg;
1569  aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.multiObjBeamFormingCfg = *aoaDspCfg->dynCfg.multiObjBeamFormingCfg;
1570  aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.prepareRangeAzimuthHeatMap = aoaDspCfg->dynCfg.prepareRangeAzimuthHeatMap;
1571  aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.staticClutterCfg = aoaDspCfg->dynCfg.staticClutterCfg;
1572  AoAProcDSP_ConvertFov(aoaDspObj, aoaDspCfg->dynCfg.fovAoaCfg);
1573 
1574  aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.extMaxVelCfg = *aoaDspCfg->dynCfg.extMaxVelCfg;
1575 
1576  /* Generate twiddle tables */
1577  AoAProcDSP_generateTables(aoaDspCfg);
1578 
1579  /* Configure EDMA */
1580  retVal = AoAProcDSP_configEDMA(aoaDspCfg);
1581  if (retVal != 0)
1582  {
1583  goto exit;
1584  }
1585 
1586 exit:
1587  return retVal;
1588 }

1591 uint32_t DPU_AoAProcDSP_process
1592 (
1593  DPU_AoAProcDSP_Handle handle,
1594  uint32_t numObjsIn,
1595  DPU_AoAProcDSP_OutParams *outParams
1596 )
1597 {
1598  volatile uint32_t startTime;
1599  volatile uint32_t waitTime = 0;
1600  int32_t retVal = 0;
1601  uint16_t idx;
1602  float range;
1603  uint32_t numObjsOut = 0;
1604 
1605  AOADspObj *aoaDspObj;
1606  DPU_AoAProcDSP_HW_Resources *res;
1607  DPU_AoAProcDSP_StaticConfig *DPParams;
1608 
1609  if (handle == NULL)
1610  {
1611  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1612  goto exit;
1613  }
1614  aoaDspObj = (AOADspObj *)handle;
1615  res = &aoaDspObj->res;
1616  DPParams = &aoaDspObj->params;
1617 
1618  startTime = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp();
1619 
1620  if (numObjsIn == 0U)
1621  {
1622  outParams->numAoADetectedPoints = numObjsIn;
1623  outParams->stats.waitTime = 0;
1624  outParams->stats.processingTime = 0;
1625  retVal = 0;
1626  goto exit;
1627  }
1628 
1629  /* Azimuth heap map */
1630  if ((aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.prepareRangeAzimuthHeatMap) && (DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim > 1))
1631  {
1632  retVal = AoAProcDSP_RangeAzimuthHeatmap(aoaDspObj,
1633  &waitTime);
1634  if (retVal != 0)
1635  {
1636  goto exit;
1637  }
1638  }
1639 
1640  /* Limit number of input samples */
1641  if (numObjsIn > res->detObjOutMaxSize)
1642  {
1643  numObjsIn = res->detObjOutMaxSize;
1644  }
1645 
1646  /* Angle estimation */
1647  if(DPParams->numVirtualAntAzim == 1)
1648  {
1649  /*If there is only one virtual antenna, there is no
1650  need of azimuth FFT as azimuth can not be estimated.*/
1651 
1652  /* Fill the output list */
1653  for(idx=0; idx < numObjsIn; idx++)
1654  {
1655  range = res->cfarRngDopSnrList[idx].rangeIdx * DPParams->rangeStep;
1656  res->detObjOut[idx].y = range;
1657  res->detObjOut[idx].x = 0.;
1658  res->detObjOut[idx].z = 0.;
1659 
1660  res->detObjOut[idx].velocity = DPParams->dopplerStep *
1661  AOA_DOPPLER_IDX_TO_SIGNED(res->cfarRngDopSnrList[idx].dopplerIdx,
1662  DPParams->numDopplerBins);
1663  res->detObjOutSideInfo[idx].snr = res->cfarRngDopSnrList[idx].snr;
1664  res->detObjOutSideInfo[idx].noise = res->cfarRngDopSnrList[idx].noise;
1665  }
1666  numObjsOut = numObjsIn;
1667  }
1668  else
1669  {
1670  retVal = AoAProcDSP_processMultipleVirtualAntennas(aoaDspObj, numObjsIn, &numObjsOut, &waitTime);
1671  if (retVal != 0)
1672  {
1673  goto exit;
1674  }
1675  }
1676 
1677  outParams->numAoADetectedPoints = numObjsOut;
1678  outParams->stats.waitTime = waitTime;
1679  outParams->stats.processingTime = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp() - startTime - waitTime;
1680 
1681 exit:
1682  return retVal;
1683 }

1685 int32_t DPU_AoAProcDSP_control
1686 (

1725  goto exit;
1726  }
1727  else
1728  {
1729  /* Save configuration */

1731  }
1732  }
1733  break;
1734  case DPU_AoAProcDSP_Cmd_ExtMaxVelocityCfg:
1735  {
1736  if((argSize != sizeof(DPU_AoAProc_ExtendedMaxVelocityCfg)) ||
1737  (arg == NULL))
1738  {
1739  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1740  goto exit;
1741  }
1742  else
1743  {
1744  /* Save configuration */

1746  }
1747  }
1748  break;
1749  case DPU_AoAProcDSP_Cmd_CompRxChannelBiasCfg:
1750  {
1751  if((argSize != sizeof(DPU_AoAProc_compRxChannelBiasCfg)) ||
1752  (arg == NULL))
1753  {
1754  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1755  goto exit;
1756  }
1757  else
1758  {
1759  /* Save configuration */
1760  memcpy((void *)&aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.compRxChanCfg, arg, argSize);

1762  }
1763  break;
1764  case DPU_AoAProcDSP_Cmd_PrepareRangeAzimuthHeatMap:
1765  {
1766  if((argSize != sizeof(bool)) ||
1767  (arg == NULL))
1768  {
1769  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1770  goto exit;
1771  }
1772  else
1773  {
1774  /* Sanity check on saved heapmap ptr and size */
1775  if ((aoaDspObj->res.azimuthStaticHeatMapSize !=
1776  (aoaDspObj->params.numRangeBins * aoaDspObj->params.numVirtualAntAzim)) ||
1777  (aoaDspObj->res.azimuthStaticHeatMap == NULL))
1778  {
1779  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1780  goto exit;
1781  }
1782 
1783  /* Save configuration */
1784  memcpy((void *)&aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.prepareRangeAzimuthHeatMap, arg, argSize);
1785  }
1786  }
1787  break;
1788 
1789  case DPU_AoAProcDSP_Cmd_staticClutterCfg:
1790  {
1791  if((argSize != sizeof(DPU_AoAProc_StaticClutterRemovalCfg)) ||
1792  (arg == NULL))
1793  {
1794  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1795  goto exit;
1796  }
1797  else
1798  {
1799  /* Update the static clutter configuration. */
1800  memcpy((void *)&aoaDspObj->dynLocalCfg.staticClutterCfg, (void *)arg, argSize);
1801  }
1802  }
1803  break;
1804 
1805  default:
1806  retVal = DPU_AOAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1807  break;
1808  }
1809 exit:
1810  return (retVal);
1811 }
